About
Travelling to Hanoi - Vietnam capital, you may be surprised by Hanoi street food - it is plentiful at everywhere that you look and is an integral part of the livelihoods of many locals. With the balance between fresh herbs and meats and a selective use of spices to reach a fine taste, the Vietnam food is various about the taste, smell and the Vietnamese food can be considered as one of the healthiest cuisines in over the world.
Hanoi, Vietnam

What tourist spot should i visit in hanoi and what food to taste?
Written March 16, 2015
HNFoodTasting
Hanoi, Vietnam
As I got your question concerning to your plan to visit Hanoi and to Hanoi Food Tasting tour, I would like to provide some travel information. Firstly, relating to Hanoi city trip, when visiting here, you should do book the hotel in Hanoi Old Quarter, it will be great to easily discover the Hanoi Old Quarter - the most touristy site in Hanoi. In addition, for a couple of days in this city, you can consider to visit inside Hanoi like Hochiminh Complex, Temple of Litterature, Hoan Kiem Lake and array of museum, mausoleum Otherwise, you should also visit outside of Hanoi with so many attractive sites: Halong bay, Hoa Lu Tam Coc or Sapa Secondly, I will back to talk about Hanoi Food Tour, in fact, this kind of tour is the short walking tour around Hanoi Old Quarter, you will have chance to meet and chat with the local people doing food business, to taste the Vietnamese food while listening the interesting information about ingredient and origin from our Food Expert your tour guide. It must be the awesome experience that can help you have a panorama about the Vietnamese food in general and Hanoi city food in particular. Thanks again and wish you have a nice time! Hanoi Food Tasting Tours Group
